=Description=

"The Manifesto Club is at the forefront of challenging the hyper-regulation of public spaces.

We produce cutting-edge research, change policy, and work at the front-line to defend those whose liberties have been affected.

We take on vetting, speech codes, leafleting bans, PSPOs, on-the-spot fines, and other key erosion of public freedoms.

We work with homeless people, buskers, young people, dog walkers, defending them against draconian powers and busybodies."

(http://manifestoclub.info/about/)

